[38;5;129m│[0m with a tool you downloaded from some shady corner of the internet.\n         [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m </p>\n    <h2>Legacy and Future</h2>\n    <p>\n        As I continue my      [38;5;129m│[0m
