[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Key Observations:**                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The protection detects `..` patterns regardless of encoding                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - It catches both relative paths and absolute traversal attempts             [32m│[0m
